3. cs.DB (Databases) - The paper deals with finding communities in large graphs, which is a common problem in database systems. 
4. cs.SOC (Computational Social Science) - The paper deals with community search in social networks, which is a common problem in computational social science. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a novel attribute relevance score function, which involves designing a machine learning model to score the relevance of attributes.
